      <title>Strengthening the Observation systems of climate change and its impacts in the Pacific, for a sustainable management of resources and adaptation   </title>
      <link>http://knowledge.cta.int/fr/Dossiers/Les-S-T-au-CTA/Evenements/Strengthening-the-Observation-systems-of-climate-change-and-its-impacts-in-the-Pacific-for-a-sustainable-management-of-resources-and-adaptation</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://pacenet.eu/" target="_self"&gt;PACE-Net Plus&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href="http://www.observatoire-gops.org/fr/;jsessionid=EAE4DE1FD51025FCC084478D55FE0E28" target="_self"&gt;GOPS&lt;/a&gt; jointly organize this workshop on climate change and its impacts due to natural variability and anthropogenic causes. Focus on three scientific and technological areas of research:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;Oceanography, ocean atmosphere interactions and variability;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;Impacts of climate change on the ecosystems and the biodiversity, on the marine and terrestrial resources;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;Impacts of climate change on societies.&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Registration: before the 15th of March 2015&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <author>francis@cta.int (Engelhard Rutger )</author>
